text: Vanessa Bayer (born November 14, 1981) is an American actress and comedian. She is best known as a cast member on Saturday Night Live from 2010 to 2017. She earned a Primetime Emmy nomination. When Bayer was a teenager, she suffered from leukemia. ==References== ==Other websites== * Category:1981 births Category:Living people Category:American movie actors Category:American television actors Category:American voice actors Category:Actors from Ohio Category:Comedians from Ohio
